&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;UNCAGE YOUR&lt;/span&gt; &lt;strong&gt;AMBITION &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;as a&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Mobile Application Coder&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;We are&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://flighthubgroup.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FlightHub Group&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, an ambitious team of people that created&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.flighthub.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FlightHub&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.justfly.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Justfly&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Our brands have grown to become two of the top-ranked travel agencies in North America. We now serve over 3 million customers per year, generating more than 3 billion dollars in sales, and we continue to grow stronger year over year. We dream big, pursue passionately, and follow through with resolute self-belief and rigorous commitment. We are a group of individuals sharing a common vision and values, having come together to pursue a collective mission: overtaking the #1 spot in the world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for a React Native Developer who works primarily through AI tools like Claude Code. You direct, review, and ship. The AI writes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Will Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work alongside an existing mobile developer to build and evolve the FlightHub app on iOS and Android using React Native&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use AI coding tools like Claude Code as your primary development method, not a supplement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Product, Design, and senior stakeholders to ship features that compete with industry leaders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement robust testing procedures and maintain high standards for code quality and performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experiment, iterate, and ship fast&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We&#39;re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of React Native development experience, with solid iOS and Android fundamentals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable doing the vast majority of coding through AI tools like Claude Code. You know how to prompt, review, and ship&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong problem-solving instincts and the confidence to make good calls in a fast-moving environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A collaborative mindset, you&#39;re joining an existing team and know how to work well with others&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bilingual in English and French&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Join FlightHub&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work on a product used by millions of real customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ship faster and learn more than in traditional dev environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be part of a team that rewards ownership and execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Real room to grow as we scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;This position is based in Montreal, Quebec and is fully on-site. The pace we move at requires real-time collaboration, not async threads.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Show us your drive and join our team!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Check us out &lt;a href=&quot;https://corporate.flighthub.com/&quot;&gt;https://corporate.flighthub.com/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align:

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;UNCAGE YOUR&lt;/span&gt; &lt;strong&gt;AMBITION &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;as a&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Unit Leader&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;We are &lt;a href=&quot;https://flighthubgroup.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FlightHub Group&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, an ambitious team of people that created &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.flighthub.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FlightHub&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.justfly.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Justfly&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Our brands have grown to become two of the top-ranked travel agencies in North America. We now serve over 3 million customers per year, generating more than 3 billion dollars in sales, and we continue to grow stronger year over year. We dream big, pursue passionately, and follow through with resolute self-belief and rigorous commitment. We are a group of individuals sharing a common vision and values, having come together to pursue a collective mission: overtaking the #1 spot in the world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This isn’t a traditional role. It&#39;s something to own and grow.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a highly driven builder to take full responsibility for a new business unit or geographic market inside FlightHub Group.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will create the product roadmap and be responsible for driving its execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll be given a real business problem, real traffic, real revenue. You will have the autonomy and accountability to figure out what works, build momentum, and scale it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Over time, you’ll build and lead a team of developers and marketers around you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Own&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full ownership of a business unit’s performance: growth, revenue, profitability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategy, roadmap, and execution: from idea to impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identifying new opportunities: markets, products, partnerships, pricing models&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Designing experiments, testing aggressively, scaling what works, killing what doesn’t&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working hands-on with Product, Engineering, Marketing, Data, and Ops to move fast&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translating business objectives into clear technical and product requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Building and leading a team as the business grows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who This Role Is For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is for someone who thrives on ownership, speed, and building from ground up.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You might come from:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data analytics or business intelligence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Software development or engineering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Product management or growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Startups, side projects, or entrepreneurial environments / backgrounds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What matters most is not your title, it’s how you operate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You are someone who:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Thinks in outcomes, not tasks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Loves digging into numbers and making decisions with even incomplete data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Moves fast, learns fast, and executes without needing permission&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wants to own something big, not just contribute to a small piece&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You Do Not Need&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A perfect resume&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Travel industry experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior P&amp;amp;L ownership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can teach the industry. We can’t teach builder energy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;UNCAGE YOUR&lt;/span&gt; &lt;strong&gt;AMBITION &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;as a&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Entry Specialist&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;We are&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://flighthubgroup.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FlightHub Group&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, an ambitious team of people that created&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.flighthub.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FlightHub&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.justfly.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Justfly&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Our brands have grown to become two of the top-ranked travel agencies in North America. We now serve over 3 million customers per year, generating more than 3 billion dollars in sales, and we continue to grow stronger year over year. We dream big, pursue passionately, and follow through with resolute self-belief and rigorous commitment. We are a group of individuals sharing a common vision and values, having come together to pursue a collective mission: overtaking the #1 spot in the world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Join our Loss Prevention team and play a key role in protecting the business while helping drive smarter, more efficient operations.&amp;nbsp;As a Data Entry Specialist, you&#39;ll ensure critical data is accurate, organized, and up to date, supporting our Chargeback, ADM, and Refund teams. You&#39;ll collaborate with teams across the business and work with airlines, merchants, suppliers, and customers to help keep operations running smoothly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;This role is perfect for someone who loves details, enjoys solving problems, and thrives in a fast-paced environment. While you&#39;ll start by focusing on data entry and operational support, you&#39;ll also have the opportunity to grow into process improvement, automation, reporting, and analytics. If you&#39;re excited about turning manual work into smarter solutions and gaining exposure to business insights, this role offers plenty of room to grow.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;What You&#39;ll Bring&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot; data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1+ year of data entry experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Travel agency or airline industry experience is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional attention to detail and accuracy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organization, communication, and problem-solving skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to handle confidential information with professionalism&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A collaborative mindset and eagerness to learn&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Enter, update, and maintain data across internal systems and databases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Verify information for accuracy and resolve discrepancies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Maintain organized records and documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Partner with internal teams to support daily operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Identify data issues, process gaps, and improvement opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Communicate professionally with internal and external stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Support collections, memo reconci

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;UNCAGE YOUR&lt;/span&gt; &lt;strong&gt;AMBITION &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;as a&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Marketing Analyst&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;We are&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://flighthubgroup.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FlightHub Group&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, an ambitious team of people that created&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.flighthub.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FlightHub&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.justfly.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Justfly&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Our brands have grown to become two of the top-ranked travel agencies in North America. We now serve over 3 million customers per year, generating more than 3 billion dollars in sales, and we continue to grow stronger year over year. We dream big, pursue passionately, and follow through with resolute self-belief and rigorous commitment. We are a group of individuals sharing a common vision and values, having come together to pursue a collective mission: overtaking the #1 spot in the world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;We are looking for a Marketing Analyst to own and grow our SEM performance on FlightHub. This is not a traditional analyst role. You will work alongside AI-powered agents that handle daily monitoring, account QA, and anomaly detection, which means your time goes toward decisions and strategy, not data pulling.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;This role is for someone who is energized by that setup. You will interpret AI-generated insights, challenge them when they look wrong, and act on them quickly. You will own outcomes, not just reports.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Will Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own SEM strategy and performance across FlightHub Canada, budget allocation, bidding direction, expansion priorities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review and act on daily AI agent reports covering spend anomalies, performance shifts, and account changes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Validate AI-generated recommendations before acting, know when to trust the output and when to dig deeper&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify gaps in agent coverage and flag edge cases that require human judgment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and measure A/B tests across acquisition levers, keywords, landing pages, bid strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with product, data, and creative teams to improve conversion funnels and tracking quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Turn performance insights into a clear roadmap and communicate findings to stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical thinker comfortable making decisions from data and navigating tradeoffs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in SEM, PPC, or performance marketing with measurable results&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable working alongside AI tools and autonomous agents, you know when to trust automated outputs and when to question them&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Curious problem-solver who digs into how things work and questions assumptions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear communicator who can explain complex findings simply to non-technical stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Thrives in a fast-paced, test-and-learn environment and takes true ownership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SQL is a plus, not a requirement, our data layer handles most standard queries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Makes This Role Different&l

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;UNCAGE YOUR&lt;/span&gt; &lt;strong&gt;AMBITION &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;as a&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Manager, Upsell&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;We are &lt;a href=&quot;https://flighthubgroup.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FlightHub Group&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, an ambitious team of people that created &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.flighthub.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FlightHub&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.justfly.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Justfly&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Our brands have grown to become two of the top-ranked travel agencies in North America. We now serve over 3 million customers per year, generating more than 3 billion dollars in sales, and we continue to grow stronger year over year. We dream big, pursue passionately, and follow through with resolute self-belief and rigorous commitment. We are a group of individuals sharing a common vision and values, having come together to pursue a collective mission: overtaking the #1 spot in the world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;We are looking for an experienced Product Manager to join our team. Working alongside Ahmad, Director of Revenue, Global Metasearch, and our technical teams, you will lead the end-to-end strategy for add-on products. Your focus will be on delivering value to customers while increasing attachment rates, revenue per booking, and cross-sell monetization across our brands.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;In this role you will be responsible for:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conducting rapid iteration, starting with prototyping, all the way through to production A/B experiments, and then full roll-out;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitoring key benchmarks, analytics, and experiment results every day to ensure the health of your product;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identifying new growth opportunities through quantitative research, UX studies, funnel analysis and reviews of industry standard methodology;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Writing the job stories, and specs for new features and improvements;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prioritizing work to ensure teams are focused on the highest value features;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Defining product strategy to improve our customers&#39; experience while using a variety of inputs, and clearly articulating the rationale behind product decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Many career paths can prepare you for this life-changing opportunity, but preferably, you’re highly skilled in:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Working in a fast-paced e-commerce environment;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Connecting with various teams and stakeholders;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Running SQL queries and analyzing data;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Designing and interpreting A/B tests;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Prioritizing needs for iteration planning, while gathering requirements and performing root-cause analysis;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Navigating complex user behaviors, and employing sound measurement to extract and design feature enhancements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;* Please note this position is in Montreal, Quebec and on-site.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Show us your drive and join our team!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;UNCAGE YOUR&lt;/span&gt; &lt;strong&gt;AMBITION &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;as an&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SEM Specialist&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;We are&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://flighthubgroup.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FlightHub Group&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, an ambitious team of people that created&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.flighthub.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FlightHub&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.justfly.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Justfly&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Our brands have grown to become two of the top-ranked travel agencies in North America. We now serve over 3 million customers per year, generating more than 3 billion dollars in sales, and we continue to grow stronger year over year. We dream big, pursue passionately, and follow through with resolute self-belief and rigorous commitment. We are a group of individuals sharing a common vision and values, having come together to pursue a collective mission: overtaking the #1 spot in the world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;We are looking for a hands-on SEM Specialist to help execute and optimize paid search campaigns that drive high-intent traffic and measurable revenue. This role is ideal for someone who enjoys working directly in Google Ads, testing ideas, analyzing performance, and learning how search impacts the business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;You’ll focus on execution, experimentation, and continuous optimization, while working closely with senior team members on larger strategy and growth initiatives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and maintain keyword lists, match types, and search terms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and run ad copy experiments to improve CTR and relevance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support landing page experiments to improve conversion rate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze Google Ads performance to identify optimization opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add and maintain negative keywords to reduce wasted spend&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor performance by device, region, and query&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with bid adjustments and budget pacing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Validate conversion tracking and flag data or tagging issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What success looks like&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Campaigns are well-structured, clean, and continuously improving&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experiments are run regularly with clear learnings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wasted spend decreases over time through smarter targeting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Performance issues and anomalies are caught early&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we’re looking for&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1–3 years of hands-on experience managing Google Ads campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical mindset and comfort working with performance data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience running ad copy and landing page tests&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid understanding of keywords, match types, and Quality Score&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Detail-oriented, organized, and comfortable owning execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Curious, eager to learn, and open to feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to have&lt;/strong&gt;
